      <td class="data-type">string</td>
      <td class="variable-desc">
      <p>Contains the sub-navigation for the requested page. A page will have sub-navigation if it is a
         parent page to other pages and is configured to show the navigation on the page. A page may
         also have sub-navigation if if is a child of a parent page that is configured to show the
         navigation on the page. Additionally, a page may be configured to have custom sub-navigation
         content.</p>
      <p>WalkerCMS fills this variable with the output from the navigation template or with the content
         of the configured custom sub-navigation..</p>
        <p>See also:</p>
